{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1063,"text":"I'm not quite sure whether\nI really want to see a snare drum"},{"time":4724,"text":"at nine o'clock or so in the morning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":6820,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":8242,"text":"But anyway, it's just great\nto see such a full theater,"},{"time":12336,"text":"and really, I must thank\nHerbie Hancock and his colleagues"},{"time":15645,"text":"for such a great presentation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18173,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":21268,"text":"One of the interesting things, of course,"},{"time":23478,"text":"is the combination of that raw hand\non the instrument and technology,"},{"time":30911,"text":"and what he said about listening\nto our young people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35575,"text":"Of course, my job is all about listening."},{"time":40094,"text":"And my aim, really,\nis to teach the world to listen."},{"time":46063,"text":"That's my only real aim in life."},{"time":50394,"text":"And it sounds quite simple,\nbut actually, it's quite a big, big job."},{"time":56555,"text":"Because you know, when you look\nat a piece of music, for example,"},{"time":61849,"text":"if I just open my little motorbike bag --"},{"time":66647,"text":"we have here, hopefully,"},{"time":69679,"text":"a piece of music that is full\nof little black dots on the page."},{"time":76494,"text":"And, you know, we open it up ..."},{"time":82732,"text":"And I read the music."},{"time":84554,"text":"So technically, I can actually read this."},{"time":89000,"text":"I will follow the instructions,\nthe tempo markings, the dynamics."},{"time":93586,"text":"I will do exactly as I'm told."},{"time":97717,"text":"And so therefore, because time is short,"},{"time":101133,"text":"if I just played you, literally,\nthe first, maybe, two lines or so --"},{"time":108738,"text":"It's very straightforward; there's nothing\ntoo difficult about the piece."},{"time":112258,"text":"But here, I'm being told\nthat the piece of music is very quick."},{"time":116550,"text":"I'm being told where to play on the drum."},{"time":119580,"text":"I'm being told which part\nof the stick to use."},{"time":123847,"text":"And I'm being told the dynamic."},{"time":126469,"text":"And I'm also being told\nthat the drum is without snares."},{"time":131094,"text":"Snares on, snares off."},{"time":134130,"text":"So therefore, if I translate\nthis piece of music,"},{"time":140006,"text":"we have this idea."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143074,"text":"(Drum sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":170823,"text":"(Drum sounds end)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":173266,"text":"And so on."},{"time":174557,"text":"My career would probably last\nabout five years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178063,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":179091,"text":"However, what I have to do as a musician"},{"time":183638,"text":"is do everything that is not on the music;"},{"time":187770,"text":"everything that there isn't time\nto learn from a teacher,"},{"time":192798,"text":"or to talk about, even, from a teacher."},{"time":196382,"text":"But it's the things you notice when\nyou're not actually with your instrument"},{"time":201259,"text":"that, in fact, become so interesting,\nand that you want to explore"},{"time":206530,"text":"through this tiny, tiny surface of a drum."},{"time":210022,"text":"So there, we experience the translation."},{"time":212747,"text":"Now we'll experience the interpretation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":217082,"text":"(Drum sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":258976,"text":"(Drum sounds end)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":262513,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":270058,"text":"Now my career may last a little longer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272793,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":274144,"text":"But in a way, you know,\nit's the same if I look at you"},{"time":277453,"text":"and I see a nice, bright young lady\nwith a pink top on."},{"time":281817,"text":"I see that you're clutching\na teddy bear, etc., etc."},{"time":285259,"text":"So I get a basic idea\nas to what you might be about,"},{"time":289841,"text":"what you might like, what you might do\nas a profession, etc., etc."},{"time":294642,"text":"However, that's just the initial idea\nI may have that we all get"},{"time":301027,"text":"when we actually look\nand we try to interpret."},{"time":304633,"text":"But actually it's so unbelievably shallow."},{"time":306957,"text":"In the same way, I look\nat the music; I get a basic idea;"},{"time":309886,"text":"I wonder what technically might be hard,\nor, you know, what I want to do."},{"time":314204,"text":"Just the basic feeling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315718,"text":"However, that is simply not enough."},{"time":318405,"text":"And I think what Herbie said:\nplease listen, listen."},{"time":322743,"text":"We have to listen\nto ourselves, first of all."},{"time":326403,"text":"If I play, for example,\nholding the stick --"},{"time":330172,"text":"where literally I do not let go\nof the stick --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":333249,"text":"(Drum sound)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":335838,"text":"you'll experience quite a lot\nof shock coming up through the arm."},{"time":339679,"text":"And you feel really quite --\nbelieve it or not --"},{"time":342028,"text":"detached from the instrument\nand from the stick,"},{"time":345295,"text":"even though I'm actually holding\nthe stick quite tightly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349441,"text":"(Drum sound)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":350890,"text":"By holding it tightly,\nI feel strangely more detached."},{"time":354871,"text":"If I just simply let go"},{"time":356612,"text":"and allow my hand, my arm,\nto be more of a support system,"},{"time":361831,"text":"suddenly --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":363053,"text":"(Drum sound)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":365091,"text":"I have more dynamic with less effort."},{"time":368572,"text":"Much more --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":369771,"text":"(Drum sound)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":371546,"text":"and I just feel, at last,\none with the stick"},{"time":374503,"text":"and one with the drum."},{"time":376186,"text":"And I'm doing far, far less."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378323,"text":"So in the same way that I need\ntime with this instrument,"},{"time":381759,"text":"I need time with people\nin order to interpret them."},{"time":387110,"text":"Not just translate them,\nbut interpret them."},{"time":389822,"text":"If, for example, I play just\na few bars of a piece of music"},{"time":397289,"text":"for which I think of myself\nas a technician --"},{"time":402703,"text":"that is, someone who is basically\na percussion player --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":406983,"text":"(Marimba sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":417973,"text":"(Marimba sounds end)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":419894,"text":"And so on, if I think of myself\nas a musician --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":423106,"text":"(Marimba sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":442867,"text":"(Marimba sounds end)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":444934,"text":"And so on."},{"time":446132,"text":"There is a little bit of a difference\nthere that is worth just --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":450018,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":452593,"text":"thinking about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454000,"text":"And I remember when I was 12 years old,"},{"time":457933,"text":"and I started playing timpani\nand percussion,"},{"time":461075,"text":"and my teacher said,"},{"time":463529,"text":"\"Well, how are we going to do this?\nYou know, music is about listening.\""},{"time":469206,"text":"And I said, \"Yes, I agree with that,\nso what's the problem?\""},{"time":473901,"text":"And he said, \"Well,\nhow are you going to hear this?"},{"time":476344,"text":"How are you going to hear that?\""},{"time":477926,"text":"And I said, \"Well, how do you hear it?\""},{"time":480507,"text":"He said, \"Well, I think\nI hear it through here.\""},{"time":484000,"text":"And I said, \"Well, I think I do too,\nbut I also hear it through my hands,"},{"time":489398,"text":"through my arms, cheekbones, my scalp,"},{"time":492961,"text":"my tummy, my chest, my legs and so on.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":496002,"text":"And so we began our lessons\nevery single time"},{"time":500858,"text":"tuning drums, in particular,\nthe kettle drums, or timpani"},{"time":504824,"text":"to such a narrow pitch interval,\nso something like --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":510606,"text":"(Marimba sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":515040,"text":"that of a difference."},{"time":516237,"text":"Then gradually:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":517463,"text":"(Marimba sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":518644,"text":"And gradually:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":519848,"text":"(Marimba sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":521663,"text":"And it's amazing that when you do\nopen your body up,"},{"time":525746,"text":"and open your hand up to allow\nthe vibration to come through,"},{"time":529745,"text":"that in fact the tiny, tiny difference --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":532092,"text":"(Marimba sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":534175,"text":"can be felt with just the tiniest\npart of your finger, there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":540281,"text":"And so what we would do\nis that I would put my hands"},{"time":543171,"text":"on the wall of the music room,"},{"time":545510,"text":"and together, we would \"listen\"\nto the sounds of the instruments,"},{"time":550728,"text":"and really try to connect\nwith those sounds"},{"time":554588,"text":"far, far more broadly\nthan simply depending on the ear."},{"time":559005,"text":"Because of course, the ear\nis subject to all sorts of things."},{"time":563672,"text":"The room we happen to be in,\nthe amplification,"},{"time":566665,"text":"the quality of the instrument,\nthe type of sticks --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":569424,"text":"(Marimba sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":575844,"text":"(Marimba sounds end)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":577815,"text":"Etc., etc., they're all different."}]},{"cues":[{"time":579658,"text":"(Marimba sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":584117,"text":"(Marimba sounds end)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":586238,"text":"Same amount of weight,\nbut different sound colors."},{"time":590847,"text":"And that's basically what we are;\nwe're just human beings,"},{"time":593775,"text":"but we all have our own\nlittle sound colors, as it were,"},{"time":596964,"text":"that make up these extraordinary\npersonalities and characters"},{"time":600637,"text":"and interests and things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":602534,"text":"And as I grew older, I then auditioned"},{"time":605558,"text":"for the Royal Academy of Music in London,"},{"time":608000,"text":"and they said, \"Well, no, we won't\naccept you, because we haven't a clue,"},{"time":612298,"text":"you know, of the future\nof a so-called 'deaf musician.'\""},{"time":616975,"text":"And I just couldn't quite accept that."},{"time":621526,"text":"And so therefore, I said to them,\n\"Well, look, if you refuse --"},{"time":628118,"text":"if you refuse me through those reasons,"},{"time":631467,"text":"as opposed to the ability to perform"},{"time":636259,"text":"and to understand and love\nthe art of creating sound --"},{"time":643000,"text":"then we have to think very, very hard\nabout the people you do actually accept.\""},{"time":649263,"text":"And as a result,\nonce we got over a little hurdle,"},{"time":653545,"text":"and having to audition twice,"},{"time":655578,"text":"they accepted me."},{"time":657817,"text":"And not only that,"},{"time":659207,"text":"what had happened was that it changed\nthe whole role of the music institutions"},{"time":664874,"text":"throughout the United Kingdom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":666850,"text":"Under no circumstances were they to refuse"},{"time":670822,"text":"any application whatsoever"},{"time":674761,"text":"on the basis of whether someone\nhad no arms, no legs --"},{"time":678293,"text":"they could still perhaps play a wind\ninstrument if it was supported on a stand."},{"time":683368,"text":"No circumstances at all\nwere used to refuse any entry."},{"time":689647,"text":"And every single entry\nhad to be listened to, experienced,"},{"time":694509,"text":"and then, based on the musical ability,"},{"time":697090,"text":"then that person\ncould either enter or not."},{"time":702366,"text":"And so therefore, this in turn meant"},{"time":705544,"text":"that there was an extremely\ninteresting bunch of students"},{"time":709205,"text":"who arrived in these various\nmusic institutions,"},{"time":712579,"text":"and I have to say, many of them now\nin the professional orchestras"},{"time":717092,"text":"throughout the world."},{"time":719095,"text":"The interesting thing\nabout this as well, though --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":721805,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":726000,"text":"is quite simply that not only were people\nconnected with sound --"},{"time":732814,"text":"which is basically all of us --"},{"time":734349,"text":"we well know that music\nreally is our daily medicine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":739295,"text":"I say \"music,\" but actually\nI mean \"sound.\""},{"time":742000,"text":"Because some of the extraordinary\nthings I've experienced as a musician --"},{"time":746649,"text":"when you may have a 15-year-old lad"},{"time":750812,"text":"who has got the most\nincredible challenges,"},{"time":755565,"text":"who may not be able\nto control his movements,"},{"time":758326,"text":"who may be deaf,\nwho may be blind, etc., etc. --"},{"time":761363,"text":"suddenly, if that young lad\nsits close to this instrument,"},{"time":767417,"text":"and perhaps even lies\nunderneath the marimba,"},{"time":770252,"text":"and you play something\nthat's so incredibly organ-like, almost --"},{"time":776000,"text":"I don't really have\nthe right sticks, perhaps --"},{"time":778884,"text":"but something like this --\nlet me change --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":784935,"text":"(Soft marimba sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":830167,"text":"(Soft marimba sounds end)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":832826,"text":"Something that's so unbelievably simple --"},{"time":835732,"text":"but he would be experiencing\nsomething that I wouldn't be,"},{"time":840076,"text":"because I'm on top of the sound."},{"time":842518,"text":"I have the sound coming this way."},{"time":844808,"text":"He would have the sound\ncoming through the resonators."},{"time":848390,"text":"If there were no resonators\non here, we would have:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":851894,"text":"(Marimba sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":858106,"text":"So he would have a fullness of sound"},{"time":860449,"text":"that those of you in the front few rows\nwouldn't experience,"},{"time":863471,"text":"those of you in the back few rows\nwouldn't experience, either."},{"time":866640,"text":"Every single one of us,\ndepending on where we're sitting,"},{"time":869757,"text":"will experience this sound\nquite, quite differently."},{"time":873558,"text":"And of course, being\nthe participator of the sound,"},{"time":876452,"text":"and that is, starting from the idea\nof what type of sound"},{"time":881302,"text":"I want to produce,\nfor example, this sound:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":885000,"text":"(No sound)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":891171,"text":"Can you hear anything?"},{"time":894108,"text":"Exactly -- because\nI'm not even touching it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":896878,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":898427,"text":"But yet, we get the sensation\nof something happening."},{"time":903078,"text":"In the same way\nthat when I see a tree moves,"},{"time":905661,"text":"then I imagine that tree\nmaking a rustling sound."},{"time":909903,"text":"Do you see what I mean?"},{"time":911153,"text":"Whatever the eye sees,\nthen there's always sound happening."},{"time":915294,"text":"So there's always, always that huge --"},{"time":919513,"text":"I mean, just this kaleidoscope\nof things to draw from."}]},{"cues":[{"time":923823,"text":"So all of my performances\nare based on entirely what I experience,"},{"time":929816,"text":"and not by learning a piece of music,"},{"time":932336,"text":"putting on someone else's\ninterpretation of it,"},{"time":934562,"text":"buying all the CDs possible\nof that particular piece of music,"},{"time":937765,"text":"and so on and so forth,"},{"time":939155,"text":"because that isn't giving me enough\nof something that is so raw and so basic,"},{"time":945531,"text":"and something that I can fully\nexperience the journey of."},{"time":950682,"text":"So it may be that, in certain halls,"},{"time":954933,"text":"this dynamic may well work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":960169,"text":"(Soft marimba sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":967370,"text":"(Soft marimba sounds end)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":969396,"text":"It may be that in other halls,"},{"time":970952,"text":"they're simply not going\nto experience that at all,"},{"time":974211,"text":"and so therefore, my level of soft,\ngentle playing may have to be --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":978443,"text":"(Marimba sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1000470,"text":"(Marimba sounds end)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1002495,"text":"Do you see what I mean?"},{"time":1003861,"text":"So, because of this explosion\nin access to sound,"},{"time":1010143,"text":"especially through the Deaf community,"},{"time":1012678,"text":"this has not only affected\nhow music institutions,"},{"time":1017129,"text":"how schools for the deaf treat sound,\nand not just as a means of therapy --"},{"time":1023922,"text":"although, of course,\nbeing a participator of music,"},{"time":1026559,"text":"that definitely is the case as well --"},{"time":1029181,"text":"but it's meant that acousticians\nhave had to really think"},{"time":1034304,"text":"about the types of halls\nthey put together."},{"time":1038350,"text":"There are so few halls in this world"},{"time":1040838,"text":"that actually have\nvery good acoustics, dare I say."},{"time":1046179,"text":"But by that I mean, where you can\nabsolutely do anything you imagine."},{"time":1051788,"text":"The tiniest, softest, softest sound\nto something that is so broad,"},{"time":1056630,"text":"so huge, so incredible."},{"time":1059376,"text":"There's always something:"},{"time":1060794,"text":"it may sound good up there,\nmay not be so good there;"},{"time":1063322,"text":"it may be great there,\nbut terrible up there;"},{"time":1065489,"text":"maybe terrible over there,\nbut not too bad there, etc., etc."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1069697,"text":"So to find an actual hall is incredible --"},{"time":1074143,"text":"for which you can play\nexactly what you imagine,"},{"time":1078243,"text":"without it being cosmetically enhanced."},{"time":1081374,"text":"So therefore, acousticians\nare actually in conversation"},{"time":1086455,"text":"with people who are hearing impaired,"},{"time":1089774,"text":"and who are participators of sound."},{"time":1094649,"text":"And this is quite interesting."},{"time":1096500,"text":"I cannot give you any detail"},{"time":1100511,"text":"as far as what is actually happening\nwith those halls,"},{"time":1104272,"text":"but it's just the fact\nthat they are going to a group of people"},{"time":1108404,"text":"for whom so many years, we've been saying,"},{"time":1112374,"text":"\"Well, how on earth can they experience\nmusic? They're deaf.\""},{"time":1115739,"text":"We go like that, and we imagine\nthat's what deafness is about."},{"time":1119078,"text":"Or we go like that, and we imagine\nthat's what blindness is about."},{"time":1122238,"text":"If we see someone in a wheelchair,\nwe assume they cannot walk."},{"time":1126084,"text":"It may be that they can walk\nthree, four, five steps."},{"time":1129632,"text":"That, to them, means they can walk."},{"time":1133594,"text":"In a year's time,\nit could be two extra steps."},{"time":1137299,"text":"In another year's time, three extra steps."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1140076,"text":"Those are hugely important\naspects to think about."},{"time":1144803,"text":"So when we do listen to each other,"},{"time":1149000,"text":"it's unbelievably important for us"},{"time":1152713,"text":"to really test our listening skills,"},{"time":1157355,"text":"to really use our bodies\nas a resonating chamber,"},{"time":1160851,"text":"to stop the judgment."},{"time":1162524,"text":"For me, as a musician who deals\nwith 99 percent of new music,"},{"time":1166419,"text":"it's very easy for me to say,"},{"time":1168367,"text":"\"Oh yes, I like that piece.\nNo, I don't like that piece,\" and so on."},{"time":1171992,"text":"And I just find that I have to give\nthose pieces of music real time."},{"time":1177145,"text":"It may be that the chemistry\nisn't quite right between myself"},{"time":1180442,"text":"and that particular piece of music,"},{"time":1182243,"text":"but that doesn't mean I have the right\nto say it's a bad piece of music."},{"time":1187077,"text":"And you know, one of the great things\nabout being a musician"},{"time":1192201,"text":"is that it is so unbelievably fluid."},{"time":1195781,"text":"So there are no rules, no right,\nno wrong, this way, that way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1200209,"text":"If I asked you to clap --\nmaybe I can do this."},{"time":1205061,"text":"If I can just say, \"Please clap\nand create the sound of thunder.\""},{"time":1211459,"text":"I'm assuming we've all\nexperienced thunder."},{"time":1214782,"text":"Now, I don't mean just the sound;"},{"time":1216388,"text":"I mean really listen\nto that thunder within yourselves."},{"time":1221329,"text":"And please try to create that\nthrough your clapping."},{"time":1223811,"text":"Try, just -- please try."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1225784,"text":"(Loud clapping sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1233561,"text":"(Clapping ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1235103,"text":"Snow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1236485,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1238645,"text":"Snow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1239837,"text":"(Soft clapping sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1242097,"text":"Have you ever heard snow?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1243666,"text":"Audience: No."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1244841,"text":"Evelyn Glennie: Well, then, stop clapping."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1247023,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1248446,"text":"Try again. Try again: snow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1252016,"text":"(No sound)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1255822,"text":"See, you're awake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1258095,"text":"Rain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1259714,"text":"(Light clapping sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1261887,"text":"EG: (Laughs)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1264354,"text":"Not bad. Not bad."},{"time":1267108,"text":"The interesting thing here, though,\nis that I asked a group of kids"},{"time":1271888,"text":"not so long ago"},{"time":1273615,"text":"exactly the same question."},{"time":1275804,"text":"Now -- great imagination,\nthank you very much."},{"time":1279207,"text":"However, not one of you got out\nof your seats to think,"},{"time":1282053,"text":"\"Right! How can I clap?"},{"time":1283744,"text":"OK, maybe:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1284990,"text":"(Clapping sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1287523,"text":"Maybe I can use my jewelry\nto create extra sounds."},{"time":1290379,"text":"Maybe I can use the other parts\nof my body to create extra sounds.\""},{"time":1294439,"text":"Not a single one of you thought\nabout clapping in a slightly different way"},{"time":1299856,"text":"other than sitting in your seats\nthere and using two hands."},{"time":1302998,"text":"In the same way, when we listen to music,"},{"time":1305167,"text":"we assume that it's all being\nfed through here."},{"time":1309132,"text":"This is how we experience music."},{"time":1311700,"text":"Of course, it's not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1313395,"text":"We experience thunder, thunder, thunder."},{"time":1316242,"text":"Think, think, think."},{"time":1317463,"text":"Listen, listen, listen."},{"time":1319852,"text":"Now, what can we do with thunder?"},{"time":1324266,"text":"I remember my teacher, when I first\nstarted, my very first lesson,"},{"time":1329684,"text":"I was all prepared\nwith sticks, ready to go."},{"time":1333093,"text":"And instead of him saying,\n\"OK, Evelyn, please, feet slightly apart,"},{"time":1337913,"text":"arms at a more or less 90-degree angle,\nsticks in a more or less V shape,"},{"time":1343777,"text":"keep this amount of space here, etc."},{"time":1346845,"text":"Please keep your back straight,\netc., etc., etc.\" --"},{"time":1349423,"text":"where I was just probably going to end up\nabsolutely rigid, frozen,"},{"time":1353611,"text":"and I would not be able to strike the drum"},{"time":1355644,"text":"because I was thinking\nof so many other things,"},{"time":1357888,"text":"he said, \"Evelyn, take this drum\naway for seven days,"},{"time":1360475,"text":"and I'll see you next week.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1362284,"text":"So -- heavens! What was I to do?"},{"time":1364713,"text":"I no longer required the sticks."},{"time":1367215,"text":"I wasn't allowed to have these sticks."},{"time":1369387,"text":"I had to basically look\nat this particular drum,"},{"time":1373048,"text":"see how it was made,"},{"time":1374745,"text":"what these little lugs did,\nwhat the snares did."},{"time":1377785,"text":"Turned it upside down,\nexperimented with the shell."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1380761,"text":"(Drum sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1382498,"text":"Experimented with the head."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1383868,"text":"(Drum sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1385354,"text":"Experimented with my body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1387158,"text":"(Drum sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1388976,"text":"Experimented with jewelry."},{"time":1390824,"text":"Experimented with all sorts of things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1392936,"text":"(Drum sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1399356,"text":"(Drum sounds end)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1403182,"text":"And of course, I returned\nwith all sorts of bruises."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1406406,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1407681,"text":"But nevertheless, it was such\nan unbelievable experience,"},{"time":1411065,"text":"because where on earth are you going\nto experience that in a piece of music?"},{"time":1415791,"text":"Where on earth are you going\nto experience that in a study book?"},{"time":1419801,"text":"So we never, ever dealt\nwith actual study books."},{"time":1423530,"text":"So for example,\none of the things that we learn"},{"time":1426210,"text":"when we are dealing\nwith being a percussion player"},{"time":1430918,"text":"as opposed to a musician,"},{"time":1432301,"text":"is basically, straightforward\nsingle-stroke rolls."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1435930,"text":"(Drum sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1439578,"text":"Like that, and then\nwe get a little faster --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1441712,"text":"(Drum sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1442904,"text":"and a little faster --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1444124,"text":"(Drum sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1445326,"text":"and a little faster,\nand so on and so forth."},{"time":1447832,"text":"What does this piece require?"},{"time":1449295,"text":"Single-stroke rolls."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1450694,"text":"(Drum sound)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1453917,"text":"So why can't I then do that\nwhilst learning a piece of music?"},{"time":1457403,"text":"And that's exactly what he did."},{"time":1460245,"text":"And interestingly, the older I became,\nand when I became a full-time student"},{"time":1465619,"text":"at a so-called \"music institution,\"\nall of that went out of the window."},{"time":1470901,"text":"We had to study from study books."},{"time":1473666,"text":"And constantly, the question, \"Well, why?\nWhy? What is this relating to?"},{"time":1477791,"text":"I need to play a piece of music.\""},{"time":1479415,"text":"\"Well, this will help your control.\""},{"time":1481196,"text":"\"Well, how? Why do I need to learn that?"},{"time":1483779,"text":"I need to relate it to a piece of music."},{"time":1486308,"text":"You know, I need to say something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1488894,"text":"Why am I practicing paradiddles?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1491024,"text":"(Drum sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1495030,"text":"Is it just literally for control,\nfor hand-stick control?"},{"time":1498921,"text":"Why am I doing that?"},{"time":1500329,"text":"I need to have the reason,"},{"time":1502753,"text":"and the reason has to be by saying\nsomething through the music.\""},{"time":1508358,"text":"And by saying something through music,\nwhich basically is sound,"},{"time":1512875,"text":"we then can reach all sorts\nof things to all sorts of people."},{"time":1517271,"text":"But I don't want to take responsibility\nof your emotional baggage."},{"time":1521544,"text":"That's up to you,\nwhen you walk through a hall,"},{"time":1523792,"text":"because that then determines\nwhat and how we listen to certain things."},{"time":1529150,"text":"I may feel sorrowful, or happy,\nor exhilarated, or angry"},{"time":1534455,"text":"when I play certain pieces of music,"},{"time":1536267,"text":"but I'm not necessarily wanting you\nto feel exactly the same thing."},{"time":1541168,"text":"So please, the next time\nyou go to a concert,"},{"time":1544296,"text":"just allow your body to open up,"},{"time":1547965,"text":"allow your body to be\nthis resonating chamber."},{"time":1551071,"text":"Be aware that you're not going\nto experience the same thing"},{"time":1554372,"text":"as the performer is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1556102,"text":"The performer is in the worst possible\nposition for the actual sound,"},{"time":1559866,"text":"because they're hearing\nthe contact of the stick --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1563446,"text":"(Drum sound)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1564982,"text":"on the drum, or the mallet\non the bit of wood,"},{"time":1567875,"text":"or the bow on the string, etc.,"},{"time":1570086,"text":"or the breath that's creating\nthe sound from wind and brass."},{"time":1574248,"text":"They're experiencing that rawness there."},{"time":1576793,"text":"But yet they're experiencing\nsomething so unbelievably pure,"},{"time":1580665,"text":"which is before the sound\nis actually happening."},{"time":1584519,"text":"Please take note of the life of the sound\nafter the actual initial strike,"},{"time":1591099,"text":"or breath, is being pulled."},{"time":1593528,"text":"Just experience the whole\njourney of that sound"},{"time":1597800,"text":"in the same way that I wished\nI'd experienced the whole journey"},{"time":1601422,"text":"of this particular conference,\nrather than just arriving last night."},{"time":1605875,"text":"But I hope maybe we can share\none or two things as the day progresses."},{"time":1610556,"text":"But thank you very much for having me!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1613319,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1619262,"text":"(Applause ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1632957,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1897631,"text":"(Music ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1903244,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}